Automotive Recovery Services, Inc.


                  Part of KAR Auction Services, Inc., Automotive Recovery Services, Inc. is a company headquartered in Carmel, IN. The firm provides auction, reconditioning, logistical, and other vehicle related services. Brian T. Clingen has been the CEO since 2007.                




