Prescient Edge Corp.

                    Prescient Edge Corp. engages in the provision of full-spectrum intelligence, technology and security offerings to corporate, federal, and international clients. It offers solutions in the areas of defense, energy, infrastructure, intelligence, surveillance, and cyber security. The firm's services include due diligence, traveler safety, federal operations and research and development. The company was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in Chicago, IL.                  




