Executive Profile
Mark J. Laskin CFAPrincipal and Portfolio Manager, BP Capital Fund Advisors, LLCAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 0 Board Members in 0 different organizations across 10 different industries.----
Background

		Mr. Mark J. Laskin, CFA, serves as the Principal and Portfolio Manager at BP Capital Fund Advisors, LLC. Prior to this, Mr. Laskin serves as Portfolio Manager of Professionally Managed Portfolios - BP Capital TwinLine Energy Fund. He served as Portfolio Manager at Morgan Stanley Investment Management Inc., Invesco Mid-Cap Value Fund, Invesco Variable Insurance Funds - Invesco V.I. Select Dimensions Balanced Fund, John Hancock Funds II - John Hancock Value Fund, Voya ... Partners, Inc. - VY Invesco Equity and Income Portfolio, Allianz Variable Insurance Products Trust - AZL Invesco Equity and Income Fund, Invesco Counselor Series Trust - Invesco Balanced Fund, Invesco Advisers, Inc., Allianz Variable Insurance Products Trust - AZL Invesco Growth and Income Fund, Invesco Fundamental Value Fund, Van Kampen Asset Management, Voya Investors Trust - VY Invesco Growth and Income Portfolio and Morgan Stanley Investment Advisors Inc. Mr. Laskin served as Portfolio Manager at ING Van Kampen Growth and Income Fund. Mr. Laskin joined the Allianz in October, 2000. Mr. Laskin served as a Member of Equity Income Team and Portfolio Manager at various funds in the fund complex of Morgan Stanley, AIM, Invesco, John Hancock Funds and ING Funds. He served as the Head of U.S. Equity Research and had also served as a Marketing Associate at Morgan Stanley, which he first joined in 1995. He was a Global Equity Analyst at Glenmede Trust. Mr. Laskin served as an International Relations Consultant at Takizawa Board of Education. He serves as Executive Director of Morgan Stanley Investment Management Inc. and Van Kampen Asset Management. He served as Executive Director and Portfolio Manager at Invesco Investment Advisers LLC, AIM Counselor Series Trust - Invesco Large Cap Relative Value Fund, Invesco Variable Insurance Funds - Invesco V.I. Income Builder Fund, Invesco V.I. Growth and Income Fund, AIM Counselor Series Trust (Invesco Counselor Series Trust) - Invesco Equity and Income Fund, AIM Variable Insurance Funds (Invesco Variable Insurance Funds) - Invesco V.I. American Value Fund, Invesco V.I. Equity and Income Fund, AIM Counselor Series Trust (Invesco Counselor Series Trust) - Invesco Growth and Income Fund and AIM Sector Funds (Invesco Sector Funds) - Invesco American Value Fund. He served as Executive Director of Invesco, AIM, AIM Sector Funds - Invesco U.S. Mid Cap Value Fund and John Hancock Funds. He holds a Chartered Financial Analyst designation. Mr. Laskin received a B.A. degree in History from Swarthmore College, and an M.B.A. degree and an M.A. degree from the Wharton School and Lauder Institute, respectively, of the University of Pennsylvania.Read Full Background




